  "section_name": "Financial Analysis",
  "text": "Profitability metrics remain robust despite revenue pressure. Q3 2025 gross margin stood at 46.49%, while operating margin reached 29.99% and net margin came in at 24.92%. EBITDA margin for the quarter was 32.82%, reflecting Apple's ability to maintain pricing power and operational efficiency even as top-line growth moderates.",
